Epic 1  :Design and Develop a Personalized Diet-Friendly Food Delivery App
User Stories:
AS an health-conscious user, I WANT to set my dietary goals and preferences (weight loss,muscle gain, specific allergies etc.) and see curated restaurant and menu recommendations based on them. (Personalized dietary goal setting and recommendations)
AS a food explorer, I WANT to discover healthy and delicious recipes within the app itself, so I can cook at home if I prefer.
(Integrated recipe library with dietary filters)
AS a calorie-conscious diner, I want to see detailed nutritional information for each menu item,
including macronutrients, calorie count, and portion sizes. (Clear and comprehensive nutritional
information)
AS a motivated dieter, I want to track my calorie intake and progress towards my goals within
the app, with visual graphs and charts. (Built-in calorie tracking and goal progress visualization)
AS an accountable individual, I want to connect with a virtual dietitian or nutritionist for
personalized guidance and support through the app. (Optional in-app dietitian/nutritionist
consultation)

Epic 2: Build a Supportive and Data-Driven Backend Infrastructure**
User Stories:
AS a data-driven dieter, I want the app to analyze my food choices and suggest healthier alternatives or portion adjustments based on my goals. (AI-powered meal suggestions and portion guidance)
As a mindful eater, I want to receive personalized reminders and nudges to stay on track with my diet throughout the day. (Personalized goal reminders and motivational notifications)
As an informed user, I want to access educational content and articles about healthy eating cooking tips, and dietary advice within the app. (Integrated educational resources and blog posts)
AS a community-oriented user, I WANT to connect with other dieters or health enthusiasts through the app for support and motivation. (Optional in-app community forum or chat groups)

As an health-focused individual, I WANT to integrate the app with my fitness tracker or health monitoring devices for holistic data analysis and progress tracking. (Optional integration with fitness trackers and health data platforms)


Epic 1: User Registration and Authentication
As a new user, I want to create an account on Nutriplanner so that I can access personalized features.
User Story 1: As a user, I want to sign up for a Nutriplanner account using my email and password.
User Story 2: As a user, I want to verify my email address to activate my account.
User Story 3: As a user, I want the option to log in with my existing social media accounts.

Epic 2: Personalized Meal Planning
As a user, I want to create personalized meal plans based on my dietary preferences and nutritional goals.
User Story 1: As a user, I want to set my dietary preferences (e.g., vegetarian, gluten-free) during account setup.
User Story 2: As a user, I want to input my nutritional goals (e.g., calorie intake, and macronutrient ratios) for meal planning.
User Story 3: As a user, I want Nutriplanner to suggest meal plans tailored to my dietary preferences and goals.

Epic 3: Food Ordering and Delivery
As a user, I want to order fresh foods and ingredients directly through the Nutriplanner app.
User Story 1: As a user, I want to browse a catalog of fresh foods and ingredients available for purchase.
User Story 2: As a user, I want to add items to my shopping cart and proceed to checkout seamlessly.
User Story 3: As a user, I want to track the status of my order and receive notifications for delivery updates.

Epic 4: Nutritional Content and Resources
As a user, I want access to educational content and resources related to nutrition and wellness.
User Story 1: As a user, I want to read articles and blogs on various nutrition topics within the Nutriplanner app.
User Story 2: As a user, I want to watch video tutorials and cooking demos for healthy recipes.
User Story 3: As a user, I want to join community forums and discussions to engage with other users and experts.

Epic 5: Community and Social Features
As a user, I want to connect with like-minded individuals and participate in wellness challenges.
User Story 1: As a user, I want to create a profile and customize my personal preferences and settings.
User Story 2: As a user, I want to follow other users and nutritionists for updates and recommendations.
User Story 3: As a user, I want to join wellness challenges and track my progress toward health goals.

Epic 6: Admin and Maintenance
As an administrator, I want tools to manage user accounts, content, and app functionality.
User Story 1: As an admin, I want access to a dashboard to monitor user activity and app performance.
User Story 2: As an admin, I want to review and moderate user-generated content to ensure quality and compliance.
User Story 3: As an admin, I want to push updates and announcements to users regarding new features and improvements.

Epic 7: Digital Wallet Integration
- User Story 1: As a user, I want to link my digital wallet to NutriPlanner for secure and convenient in-app transactions.

Epic 8: Vendor and Farmers Market Integration
- User Story 1: As a user, I want NutriPlanner to source fresh and local produce from exclusive vendors and farmers markets.

Epic 9: Testing and Quality Assurance
- User Story 1: As a user, I expect NutriPlanner to provide a seamless and bug-free experience during app usage.

Epic 10: Marketing and Launch
- User Story 1: As a user, I want to be informed about NutriPlanner's launch through engaging marketing campaigns.

Epic 11: Monitoring and Feedback
- User Story 1: As a user, I want to provide feedback on meals, services, and overall user experience through surveys.

Epic 3: Meal Ordering and Scheduling
- User Story 1: As a user, I want to browse through a variety of healthy meals and snacks available on NutriPlanner.
- User Story 2: As a user, I want to schedule my meal orders in advance, specifying delivery times that suit my daily routine.
- User Story 3: As a user, I want to receive timely notifications and updates on my scheduled meal deliveries.



